         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper we generalize the method of Wildanger for finding small solutions to unit equations to the case of S-unit equations. The method uses a minor generalization of the LLL based techniques used to reduce the bounds derived from transcendence theory, followed by an enumeration strategy based on the Fincke-Pohst algorithm. The method used reduces the computing time needed from MIPS years down to minutes.</p>
          </abstract>
